Potential deaths averted in USA by replacing cigarettes with e-cigarettes.

Levy DT(1), Borland R(2), Lindblom EN(3), Goniewicz ML(4), Meza R(5), Holford 
TR(6), Yuan Z(7), Luo Y(7), O'Connor RJ(4), Niaura R(8), Abrams DB(1)(8).

