Chang CK(1), Lin YY(2), Wong PC(3), Kao HC(4), Chen HY(1), Lee SH(5), Cheng 
CK(6).

Author information:
(1)The Rehabilitation Center, Taipei Veterans General Hospital, Taipei, Taiwan, 
ROC.
(2)Department of Biomedical Engineering, National Yang-Ming University, Taipei, 
Taiwan, ROC.
(3)Department of Biomedical Engineering, National Yang-Ming University, Taipei, 
